casebody.data:
GREGORY REED AND ASSOCIATES, P.C., Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
Elaine STEELE, Personal Representative of the Estate of Rosa Louise Parks, Deceased, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 157694
COA: 335939 Supreme Court of Michigan. December 4, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the March 20, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
